# Button Controlled LED (Arduino Simulation)

This project demonstrates digital input handling using a push button to control an LED.

## Concepts Covered
- Digital input using push button
- INPUT_PULLUP configuration
- Conditional logic using if-else
- Digital output control

## Working
- LED turns ON when the button is pressed
- LED turns OFF when the button is released

## Tools Used
- Arduino (Simulation)
- Tinkercad Circuits
